Package frc.misc

Interface ISubsystem

All Known Subinterfaces:
IDistanceSensor, IVision
All Known Implementing Classes:
AbstractAutonManager, AbstractIMU, ArticulatedHood, AutonManager, AutonManager, AutonManager, BallPhoton, Chirp, DriveManager, GoalLimelight, GoalPhoton, Hopper, Intake, RevDistanceSensor, RobotTelemetry, Shooter, Turret, WrappedNavX2IMU, WrappedPigeonIMU
public interface ISubsystem
The generic layout for any subsystem. Ensures that any subsystem on the robot has the appropriate fields
Author:
jojo2357
